The original version of kafka-perf-tools can be obtained from: https://github.com/jkorab/ameliant-tools
Checkout: 19-June-2017

Main changes compared to the original version:
- FileDriver loads from an InputStream instantiated from a resource local to the jar
- FileDriver can load a single message or a sequence of messages (one-by-one)
- ProducerDriver can repeat a single message or a sequence of messages, cycling from the beginning when the sequence has been completed.

